#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.70"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.70:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.70:0.2"
msgid "7. Yamakavagga "
msgstr "7. Pairs "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.70:0.3"
msgid "70. Dutiyakathāvatthusutta "
msgstr "70. Topics of Discussion (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.70:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.70:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena sambahulā bhikkhū pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantā upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ sannisinnā sannipatitā anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ anuyuttā viharanti, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "Now at that time, after the meal, on return from alms-round, several mendicants sat together in the meeting hall. "

msgctxt "an10.70:1.3"
msgid "rājakathaṃ corakathaṃ mahāmattakathaṃ … pe … itibhavābhavakathaṃ iti vāti. "
msgstr "They engaged in all kinds of unworthy talk, such as talk about kings, bandits, and ministers; talk about armies, threats, and wars; talk about food, drink, clothes, and beds; talk about garlands and fragrances; talk about family, vehicles, villages, towns, cities, and nations; talk about women and heroes; street talk and well talk; talk about the departed; miscellaneous talk; tales of land and sea; and talk about being reborn in this or that state of existence. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.130, sc2
msgctxt "an10.70:2.1"
msgid "“Dasayimāni, bhikkhave, pāsaṃsāni ṭhānāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are ten grounds for praise. "

msgctxt "an10.70:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni dasa? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.70:2.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu attanā ca appiccho hoti, appicchakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant personally has few wishes, and speaks to the mendicants on having few wishes. "

msgctxt "an10.70:2.4"
msgid "‘Appiccho bhikkhu appicchakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (1) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.70:3.1"
msgid "Attanā ca santuṭṭho hoti, santuṭṭhikathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is content, and speaks to the mendicants on contentment. "

msgctxt "an10.70:3.2"
msgid "‘Santuṭṭho bhikkhu santuṭṭhikathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (2) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.70:4.1"
msgid "Attanā ca pavivitto hoti, pavivekakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is secluded, and speaks to the mendicants on seclusion. "

msgctxt "an10.70:4.2"
msgid "‘Pavivitto bhikkhu pavivekakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (3) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.70:5.1"
msgid "Attanā ca asaṃsaṭṭho hoti, asaṃsaṭṭhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally doesn’t mix closely with others, and speaks to the mendicants on not mixing closely with others. "

msgctxt "an10.70:5.2"
msgid "‘Asaṃsaṭṭho bhikkhu asaṃsaṭṭhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (4) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.70:6.1"
msgid "Attanā ca āraddhavīriyo hoti, vīriyārambhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is energetic, and speaks to the mendicants on being energetic. "

msgctxt "an10.70:6.2"
msgid "‘Āraddhavīriyo bhikkhu vīriyārambhakathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (5) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.70:7.1"
msgid "Attanā ca sīlasampanno hoti, sīlasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is accomplished in ethics, and speaks to the mendicants on being accomplished in ethics. "

msgctxt "an10.70:7.2"
msgid "‘Sīlasampanno bhikkhu sīlasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (6) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.70:8.1"
msgid "Attanā ca samādhisampanno hoti, samādhisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is accomplished in immersion, and speaks to the mendicants on being accomplished in immersion. "

msgctxt "an10.70:8.2"
msgid "‘Samādhisampanno bhikkhu samādhisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (7) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an10.70:9.1"
msgid "Attanā ca paññāsampanno hoti, paññāsampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is accomplished in wisdom, and speaks to the mendicants on being accomplished in wisdom. "

msgctxt "an10.70:9.2"
msgid "‘Paññāsampanno bhikkhu paññāsampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (8) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.70:10.1"
msgid "Attanā ca vimuttisampanno hoti, vimuttisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is accomplished in freedom, and speaks to the mendicants on being accomplished in freedom. "

msgctxt "an10.70:10.2"
msgid "‘Vimuttisampanno bhikkhu vimuttisampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (9) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an10.70:11.1"
msgid "Attanā ca vimuttiñāṇadassanasampanno hoti, vimuttiñāṇadassanasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā hoti. "
msgstr "A mendicant personally is accomplished in the knowledge and vision of freedom, and speaks to the mendicants on being accomplished in the knowledge and vision of freedom. "

msgctxt "an10.70:11.2"
msgid "‘Vimuttiñāṇadassanasampanno bhikkhu vimuttiñāṇadassanasampadākathañca bhikkhūnaṃ kattā’ti pāsaṃsametaṃ ṭhānaṃ. (10) "
msgstr "This is a ground for praise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an10.70:12.1"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, dasa pāsaṃsāni ṭhānānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the ten grounds for praise.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.70:12.2"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.70:12.3"
msgid "Yamakavaggo dutiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.131, sc13
msgctxt "an10.70:13.1"
msgid "Avijjā taṇhā niṭṭhā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.70:13.2"
msgid "avecca dve sukhāni ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.70:13.3"
msgid "Naḷakapāne dve vuttā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.70:13.4"
msgid "kathāvatthūpare duveti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
